  "identifier": "HB 609",
  "title": "AN ACT relating to classroom libraries and making an appropriation therefor.",
  "abstract": "Create a new section of KRS Chapter 158 to define terms; establish the Classroom Library Grant Program; provide that the Kentucky Department of Education to implement the grant program through selection of a program administrator; establish the qualifications and duties of the program administrator; appropriate $5,000,000 from the General Fund to implement the Classroom Library Grant Program; APPROPRIATION.",
